{Speech 1 Answer 105}{}{Arrived in NCR.}
{Speech 1 Answer 113}{}{Arrived in NCR and agreed to go back.}
{Speech 1 Answer 112}{}{Arrived in NCR and refused to go back.}
{Speech 1 Answer 106}{}{Returned to Redding, wants the reward for the second caravan. In this branch you can take the escort quest again.}
{Speech 1 Answer 106*}{}{Returned to Redding, wants the reward for the second caravan. In this branch you can take the escort quest again.}
{Speech 1 Answer 101}{}{That bastard ran off from the caravan!}
{Speech 1 Answer 102}{}{That bastard tried to rob the caravan!}
{Speech 1 Answer 103}{}{This man died defending the caravan!}
{Speech 1 Answer 104}{}{The guide was killed during the caravan}
{Speech 1 Answer 4}{}{can take the caravan quest}
